entry.title: joaopauloschuler/neural-api
entry.summary: CAI NEURAL API - Pascal based neural network API optimized for AVX, AVX2 and AVX512 instruction sets plus OpenCL capable devices including AMD, Intel and NVIDIA.

entry.title: skia4delphi/skia4delphi
entry.summary: Skia4Delphi is a cross-platform 2D graphics API for Delphi platforms based on Google's Skia Graphics Library. It provides a comprehensive 2D API that can be used across mobile, server and desktop models to render images.
